high_descs: Turn left and walk to the left side of the counter.
Take the bar of soap out of the left sink basin.
Turn around to face the toilet.
Put the bar of soap on the front right edge of the toilet tank.
Turn around and look down.
Open the leftmost cabinet door below the counter and take out the bar of soap then close the cabinet.
Turn around and face the toilet.
Put the bar of soap on top of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Move two bars of soap to a toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn left, go forward a bit, turn left, go to the wall, turn right
Pick up the soap in the sink
Turn around and go to the toilet
Put the soap on the flusher
Turn around and face the sink
Open the cupboard on the left, pick up the soap, close the cupboard
Turn around and go to the toilet
Put the soap on the flusher
anns.task_desc: Put two soap bars on the flusher

high_descs: Turn left, hang a left at the counter and turn right at the wall to face the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap from inside the sink.
Turn around to face the white toilet.
Put the bar of soap on the toilet tank in front of the gold soap bottle on the right side.
Turn around to face the cabinets underneath the sink on the vanity.
Open the lower left cabinet under the sink, pick up the bar of soap inside and close the door.
Turn around to face the white toilet.
Put the bar of soap on the toilet tank in the front middle in between the gold roll and the other bar of soap.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap on a toilet tank.
